 \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his team-player attitude\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead leg\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"an unimpressive split\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 326}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 335}, {\"ngram\": \"the full beam\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But O'Donnell had an outstanding championship performance in the Italian capital that should be applauded.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9907585078387324, \"rank\": 0.009254081028030006, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"an outstanding championship performance\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A semi-finalist in the individual 400m event, where he subsequently got disqualified for a lane infringement, running a significant season's best in the heats on no sleep, and lining up again for the men's 4x400m relay was no mean physical feat.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finalist\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 525}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual 400m\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"event\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"a lane infringement\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"no sleep\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 4x400m relay\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"no mean physical feat\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Sharlene Mawdsley managed to out-do the Sligo man on the number of 400m races run over the six-day event, but he says it did take a toll.\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9996530076331981, \"rank\": 0.00034711281145302473, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only Sharlene Mawdsley\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"400m races\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"the six-day event\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a toll\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was definitely the quickest week of my life and a part of that was, I got probably two or three nights worth of sleep in that whole week,\\\" O'Donnell told RT\\u00c9 Sport of the aftermath of winning on the international stage.. \\\"I came back, people were still asking me when I came home if I was wrecked or not ,and I was, 'No, I am actually absolutely fine'.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1061, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999999789533833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the quickest week\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"sleep\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1024}, {\"ngram\": \"that whole week\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"the aftermath\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was still on a high for a few days when I came home, and then to be fair it did hit me a few days later.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a high\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran one race, 46.0, I just was not at my best.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one race\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I picked up a little bit of an illness and I was running through that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"an illness\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Sligo native is currently 79th on the Paris ranking list and only the top 48 will make the start line in the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1498, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9996530076331981, \"rank\": 0.00034711281145302473, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}, {\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.7628741220435945e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donnell's last chance to qualify will be at Sunday's National Championships at the Morton Stadium in Santry, and he will need the automatic qualification mark of 45.00 seconds.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.335608886483529e-17, \"text\": \"National Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finglas\", \"score\": 0.9681662542645637, \"rank\": 0.032880444260225496, \"text\": \"Santry\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finglas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finglas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell's last chance\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the Morton Stadium\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"the automatic qualification mark\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1785}, {\"ngram\": \"45.00 seconds\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donnell has raced only four times individually this year, leaving his world ranking lagging.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1814}, {\"ngram\": \"only four times\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"his world ranking lagging\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a system that rewards racing often and in meetings that are hard to access with no agent backing, athletes like O'Donnell that either have no agent or are fighting injury are on the backfoot.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a system\", \"from\": 1903, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"meetings\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1953}, {\"ngram\": \"no agent backing\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"no agent\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"the backfoot\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The rankings have not worked out for me this year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The rankings\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like it's just a case of who has the best agent and I have no agent.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just a case\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"the best agent\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"no agent\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still think that I am capable of doing it and if not, hopefully, I'd still be delighted to be on the relay.\\\"\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The required time of is 0.25 of a second faster than his best, which was set in 2022, and would put him second on the Irish all-time list, behind David Gillick.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2460, \"end\": 2465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999998466901279, \"rank\": 1.5227900577376494e-07, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"David Gillick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Gillick\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The required time\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He missed out on several weeks racing at the beginning of the season due to travelling to the World Relays in the Bahamas, where he wasn't selected for the final team that claimed bronze.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999999896044756, \"rank\": 9.681941920577181e-09, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several weeks\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2534}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Relays\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"the final team\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Testament to his character, O'Donnell did not let it effect him for long.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his character\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the Bahamas, obviously it was disappointing not to be picked for that, it was a bit of a shock, but I could have spent the next few months sulking about that but I decided not to.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2776, \"end\": 2783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999999896044756, \"rank\": 9.681941920577181e-09, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"a shock\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few months\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I decided to just knuckle down and run as fast as I could.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have put down a pretty decent marker in 45.6.\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pretty decent marker\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd like to think that puts me in a good spot (for the mixed relay) and I have a lot of experience, but at the same time, I want to qualify individually and I have got one more shot to do that,\\\" he admitted.\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good spot\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3108}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3129}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"experience\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"one more shot\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final team for the World Relays was likely picked on indoor performances, which the 26-year-old admits is not his forte.\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The final team\", \"from\": 3272, \"to\": 3286}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Relays\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"indoor performances\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"the 26-year-old admits\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3378}, {\"ngram\": \"his forte\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually did race once, it's not on my World Athletics profile, it was very low key.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3440, \"end\": 3455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999895435394, \"rank\": 1.0456625393563117e-08, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"very low key\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran 48 seconds, which obviously is not good enough, but I do that every year.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you look back I have a huge discrepancy between my indoor and outdoor times.\", \"from\": 3566, \"to\": 3645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a huge discrepancy\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"my indoor and outdoor times\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every year when I open up I do get a bit of a laugh.\", \"from\": 3647, \"to\": 3700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3683, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"a laugh\", \"from\": 3692, \"to\": 3699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People see me run 48 or 47s and say 'It's not going to be his year, he's not in shape this year' but I never lose any confidence.\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3707}, {\"ngram\": \"47s\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3728}, {\"ngram\": \"his year\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"shape\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"any confidence\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not run round those bends indoors,\\\" he laughs.\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3883, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those bends indoors\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still put myself out there and I still race and I am not afraid to sell myself short eventually, because that's what I am doing, I am going out there and selling myself short.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did that this year but the way my running style is and the way my training programme is that it's based on outdoors, and I am good at the right times I think.\\\"\", \"from\": 4065, \"to\": 4227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my running style\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ngram\": \"my training programme\", \"from\": 4131, \"to\": 4152}, {\"ngram\": \"the right times\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been quite the journey for O'Donnell, who has been a key part of the mixed relay success since the first event in 2021, where he ran the anchor leg to qualify the team for the Olympics in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4426, \"end\": 4431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9063977787544915, \"rank\": 0.10326836998767329, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite the journey\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4260}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"a key part\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4299}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay success\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4326}, {\"ngram\": \"the first event\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"the anchor leg\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4385}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4422}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since then the mixed 4x400m team has been on the rise, making Olympic and World finals, and now they areEuropean gold medallists,all with O'Donnell as part of the squad.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mixed 4x400m team\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4466}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 4479, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic and World finals\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medallists\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4562}, {\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 4572, \"to\": 4581}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He explains it has not always been a given.\", \"from\": 4604, \"to\": 4647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started off with this team and almost every time we step foot on a track, we have been successful.\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4750, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 4669, \"to\": 4678}, {\"ngram\": \"foot\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4713}, {\"ngram\": \"a track\", \"from\": 4717, \"to\": 4724}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it started off by qualifying for the Olympics and then it was making Olympic finals, making World finals and while we were kind of scraping into those finals it was a bit of a miracle job.\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4788, \"to\": 4800}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic finals\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4838}, {\"ngram\": \"World finals\", \"from\": 4847, \"to\": 4859}, {\"ngram\": \"those finals\", \"from\": 4900, \"to\": 4912}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4925}, {\"ngram\": \"a miracle job\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every time we have been together it's been such a high.\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 5001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a high\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 5000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time has been even more of a high which is hard to explain because when we first made that Olympic final, when we first qualified for the Olympics, that high was crazy but this (winning European gold) was even on another level,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 5002, \"to\": 5244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This time\", \"fro