am\": \"the mixed 4x400m\", \"from\": 6690, \"to\": 6706}, {\"ngram\": \"a relay medal\", \"from\": 6760, \"to\": 6773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donnell admits that having the European silver medallist on the team would be ideal, but is pragmatic about that possibility.\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 6776, \"to\": 6785}, {\"ngram\": \"the European silver medallist\", \"from\": 6805, \"to\": 6834}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 6838, \"to\": 6846}, {\"ngram\": \"that possibility\", \"from\": 6886, \"to\": 6902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We just have to do our thing and try run the best ourselves,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6905, \"to\": 6976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our thing\", \"from\": 6925, \"to\": 6934}, {\"ngram\": \"the best ourselves\", \"from\": 6947, \"to\": 6965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, it's not a secret that we'd love her to run but that's a decision to be made by herself and her coaches and whatever they think is best.\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 7125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a secret\", \"from\": 6998, \"to\": 7006}, {\"ngram\": \"a decision\", \"from\": 7044, \"to\": 7054}, {\"ngram\": \"her coaches\", \"from\": 7081, \"to\": 7092}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 7097, \"to\": 7105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she does not run, we have made finals before without her.\", \"from\": 7126, \"to\": 7186, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 7160, \"to\": 7166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got good athletes to step up.\", \"from\": 7187, \"to\": 7224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good athletes\", \"from\": 7199, \"to\": 7212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, we'd like her to run but then again, she's going to make whatever decision is best for her.\", \"from\": 7226, \"to\": 7329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever decision\", \"from\": 7295, \"to\": 7312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will not be any grudges held over that but all we can do between now and then is try and improve ourselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 7330, \"to\": 7444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any grudges\", \"from\": 7348, \"to\": 7359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not all athletes have the same mindset, but both himself and Mawdsley stand out as true relay runners that love nothing more than running for their team and country.\", \"from\": 7446, \"to\": 7611, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not all athletes\", \"from\": 7446, \"to\": 7462}, {\"ngram\": \"the same mindset\", \"from\": 7468, \"to\": 7484}, {\"ngram\": \"Mawdsley\", \"from\": 7507, \"to\": 7515}, {\"ngram\": \"true relay runners\", \"from\": 7529, \"to\": 7547}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 7558, \"to\": 7565}, {\"ngram\": \"their team\", \"from\": 7588, \"to\": 7598}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 7603, \"to\": 7610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has a proven record of progressing to individuals semi-finals in the days following the mixed 4x400m, first in the World Championships in Oregon in 2022 and again in Rome this year.\", \"from\": 7612, \"to\": 7796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7754, \"end\": 7760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.999917703371061, \"rank\": 8.17525184210961e-05, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 7782, \"end\": 7786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9854593028492804, \"rank\": 0.014755089935228652, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a proven record\", \"from\": 7619, \"to\": 7634}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 7653, \"to\": 7664}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 7670, \"to\": 7676}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 7680, \"to\": 7688}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed 4x400m\", \"from\": 7699, \"to\": 7715}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 7726, \"to\": 7749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donnell does not find it difficult sacrificing his own performance in his individual event.\", \"from\": 7798, \"to\": 7891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 7798, \"to\": 7807}, {\"ngram\": \"his own performance\", \"from\": 7847, \"to\": 7866}, {\"ngram\": \"his individual event\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A medal is a medal at the end of it.\", \"from\": 7892, \"to\": 7928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A medal\", \"from\": 7892, \"to\": 7899}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 7903, \"to\": 7910}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 7914, \"to\": 7921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get asked the question a lot 'Would you rather be a finalist or a relay medallist?'.\", \"from\": 7930, \"to\": 8017, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 7943, \"to\": 7955}, {\"ngram\": \"a finalist\", \"from\": 7983, \"to\": 7993}, {\"ngram\": \"a relay medallist\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an absolute no-brainer, it would be the medal all day long.\", \"from\": 8018, \"to\": 8082, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an absolute no-brainer\", \"from\": 8023, \"to\": 8045}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 8059, \"to\": 8068}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, I have tended to prioritise the relay on the basis of that.\", \"from\": 8083, \"to\": 8158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 8088, \"to\": 8097}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay\", \"from\": 8127, \"to\": 8136}, {\"ngram\": \"the basis\", \"from\": 8140, \"to\": 8149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even this year as well, I have probably taken a hit on my individual Olympic hopes.\", \"from\": 8160, \"to\": 8244, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hit\", \"from\": 8207, \"to\": 8212}, {\"ngram\": \"my individual Olympic\", \"from\": 8216, \"to\": 8237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to the Bahamas for a few weeks, losing a lot of time there with jet-lag and I was unable to run individually in those big races.\", \"from\": 8245, \"to\": 8380, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8260, \"end\": 8267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 0.9999999896044756, \"rank\": 9.681941920577181e-09, \"text\": \"Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few weeks\", \"from\": 8271, \"to\": 8282}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 8291, \"to\": 8296}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 8300, \"to\": 8304}, {\"ngram\": \"jet-lag\", \"from\": 8316, \"to\": 8323}, {\"ngram\": \"those big races\", \"from\": 8364, \"to\": 8379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Even still at the Europeans, it was the priority and I have absolutely no regrets because we are getting success with that.\", \"from\": 8382, \"to\": 8506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Europeans\", \"from\": 8397, \"to\": 8410}, {\"ngram\": \"the priority\", \"from\": 8419, \"to\": 8431}, {\"ngram\": \"no regrets\", \"from\": 8454, \"to\": 8464}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 8488, \"to\": 8495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me a medal, all day, that's something I am hopefully going to show the grandchildren and something to look back on and put on the CV.\\\"\", \"from\": 8507, \"to\": 8645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 8514, \"to\": 8521}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8539, \"to\": 8548}, {\"ngram\": \"the grandchildren\", \"from\": 8578, \"to\": 8595}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8600, \"to\": 8609}, {\"ngram\": \"the CV\", \"from\": 8637, \"to\": 8643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donnell played soccer in his teenage years for Benbulben FC and was picked to play for Sligo/Leitrim Youth Schoolboys League at the prestigious Kennedy Cup in 2012.\", \"from\": 8647, \"to\": 8813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8697, \"end\": 8706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benbulbin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Benbulben\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benbulbin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benbulbin\"}, {\"begin\": 8737, \"end\": 8742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"score\": 0.9996530076331981, \"rank\": 0.00034711281145302473, \"text\": \"Sligo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sligo\"}, {\"begin\": 8743, \"end\": 8750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Leitrim\", \"score\": 0.9999991131257342, \"rank\": 8.868735275725655e-07, \"text\": \"Leitrim\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Leitrim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/County_Leitrim\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donnell\", \"from\": 8647, \"to\": 8656}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 8664, \"to\": 8670}, {\"ngram\": \"his teenage years\", \"from\": 8674, \"to\": 8691}, {\"ngram\": \"the prestigious Kennedy Cup\", \"from\": 8777, \"to\": 8804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An experience that may have some influence on his selfless choices on the track.\", \"from\": 8814, \"to\": 8894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An experience\", \"from\": 8814, \"to\": 8827}, {\"ngram\": \"some influence\", \"from\": 8842, \"to\": 8856}, {\"ngram\": \"his selfless choices\", \"from\": 8860, \"to\": 8880}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 8884, \"to\": 8893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love being part of a team,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 8896, \"to\": 8935, \